tiers.ability_description: Whenever Light Side allies start their turn, for each enemy with fewer than 4 debuffs, that ally gains 30% Potency until the end of the turn.
Whenever Dark Side allies start their turn, for each enemy with fewer than 4 debuffs, that ally gains 30% Potency until the end of the turn.
The first time each Tusken ally falls below 50% Health, all Tusken allies reduce their cooldowns by 1 and gain 10% Turn Meter.
Light Side allies recover 2% Health whenever they critically hit an enemy.
Whenever Dark Side allies grant a buff to another ally, that other ally recovers 3% Health and Protection.
Dark Side allies recover 2% Health whenever they critically hit an enemy.
The first time each Tusken ally falls below 50% Health they gain Damage Immunity for 1 turn and gain Health Steal Up for 2 turns.
Whenever Dark Side allies grant a buff to another ally, that other ally recovers 3% Health and Protection.
Whenever Dark Side allies grant a buff to another ally, that other ally recovers 3% Health and Protection.

The first time each Hutt Cartel ally falls below 50% Health, they gain Damage Immunity for 1 turn, which can't be copied, dispelled, or prevented.\n\nWhenever an enemy takes damage from a Thermal Detonator expiring, Hutt Cartel allies recover 5% Health and Protection, gain 5% Turn Meter, and there is a 50% chance that enemy is inflicted with a Thermal Detonator for 2 turns, which can't be dispelled, prevented, or resisted.

The max cooldown of Inventive is reduced by 1. Whenever Boushh inflicts Thermal Detonators on an enemy, inflict an additional Thermal Detonator for 2 turns and Hutt Cartel allies gain 10% Armor Penetration (max 70%) and 10% Turn Meter (once per turn).
Light Side allies recover 2% Health whenever they critically hit an enemy.
Whenever a Scoundrel ally deals damage to an enemy and no other enemy is Blinded, inflict Blind for 2 turns on the enemy, which can't be resisted.
Whenever Light Side allies start their turn, for each enemy with fewer than 4 debuffs, that ally gains 30% Potency until the end of the turn.
Light Side allies recover 2% Health whenever they critically hit an enemy.
Whenever Light Side allies grant a buff to another ally, that other ally recovers 3% Health and Protection.
Whenever Dark Side allies gain a buff, they recover 2% Health and Protection.
Whenever Empire allies critically hit an enemy during their turn, that ally gains 10% Offense (stacking) for 2 turns.

At the start of battle and whenever Dark Trooper Moff Gideon uses a Special ability, if the allied slot is available and there is no ally Dark Trooper, summon a Dark Trooper. Otherwise, a summoned ally Dark Trooper gains a stack of Dark Trooper Squad.\n\nWhenever an ally uses a Special ability, all Moff Gideons gain a stack of Insight. Imperial Remnant allies have +15% Defense and Offense for each stack of Insight on Moff Gideons.
Whenever Light Side allies inflict a debuff, they gain 2% Critical Chance (stacking) for 3 turns.
Whenever Dark Side allies gain a buff, they recover 2% Health and Protection.
At the start of their first turn, Empire allies gain Offense equal to 400% of their current Defense. Then they lose 50% Defense.
Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff, they gain 2% Critical Chance (stacking) for 3 turns.
At the end of their turn, Empire allies gain Defense Penetration Up and Offense Up for 1 turn.
